Class SheetConverter

java.lang.Object
  org.adorsys.xlseasy.impl.converter.SheetConverter
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.adorsys.xlseasy.annotation.ICellConverter, CollectionElementConverter
public class SheetConverter
extends Object
implements org.adorsys.xlseasy.annotation.ICellConverter, CollectionElementConverter

Extending this converter with a key field, because converter shall not automatically discover key field using @Key annotation. This, there will be no singleton, each sheet will carry proper converter.

Author:
francis
